{
  "stem": "9262.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We got salt, and other things, which were the bare necessities.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Other members of the family also went.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But my father saw that, in addition to what we had, we should try to get freshly baked bread as well.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was a necessity.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We just couldn't rely on using up our flour to bake bread.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We really should go and get bread.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my brother, myself, and also my father, we used to stay in the queues to get bread, and we were only allocated one loaf per person.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So we came home.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And of course, people started hoarding because they knew the war broke out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Water we had in the beginning in our tap.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When war broke out, the first and second day we had to go down to the courtyard and put a bucket down in the well to bring the water up.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's the way they usually have in Poland.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You have a house, and in each courtyard you have like a little well.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in an emergency, you can always put the bucket down and bring it up, and you would have fresh water.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's what we did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had to use it for cooking and for sanitation, because the toilets, at the time, were blocked.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were not functioning.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Everything came to a standstill.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The electricity was on.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, electricity was on, and we had gas cooking, so the gas was on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It wasn't bombed at the time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Coal fires we didn't have because we run out of coal.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So it was cold.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And already in September we were wearing two overcoats, two jackets, because we had nothing to warm ourselves.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And each day, we heard the Germans were coming nearer.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were fighting here and fighting there.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
